WEBVTT

00:03:28.830 --> 00:03:33.470
used to walk around town
with his gun in his holster,

00:03:33.494 --> 00:03:38.449
and people knew if you messed with
Mr. Parks's children or grandchildren,

00:03:38.473 --> 00:03:42.684
he would put a cap
in your proverbial bottom."

00:03:42.708 --> 00:03:43.910
(Laughter)

00:03:43.934 --> 00:03:45.094
Right?

00:03:45.118 --> 00:03:47.437
He was not someone to mess with.

00:03:47.922 --> 00:03:53.790
And he said, "I also learned
that Rosa Parks married a man in Raymond

00:03:53.814 --> 00:03:56.977
who was a lot like her grandfather."

00:03:57.884 --> 00:03:59.329
He would organize.

00:03:59.353 --> 00:04:01.669
He was a civil rights activist.